Auth -> As a user, you should be able to ->
Sign up/register for an account
Edit the profile the sign up creates
Remove the account if no longer needed

Posts -> as a user, you should be able to ->
Create a new post
Edit any post you have created
Add an image to a post
Delete the post if needed

Animals -> as a user, you should be able to ->
Add a new animal linked to your profile
Edit the information of that animal
Add images for that animal
Remove the animal profile if needed
